The paper proposes a clustering framework that integrates supervised learning on unlabeled data. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to machine learning and data mining. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.DM (Data Mining) are all potential sub-categories for this paper.
